):

1. *Zaustavi* sam se kod prodavnice da kupim par stvari. (I stopped at the store to buy a few things.)
2. Nisam znao da *zaustavim* auto na vreme. (I didn't know how to stop the car in time.)
3. On joj je *zaustavio* ruku da bi je obuhvatio oko struka. (He stopped her hand to wrap it around his waist.)
4. *Zaustavio* je taksi da bi se ukrcao. (He stopped a taxi to get in.)
5. Policija je *zaustavila* sve automobile na putu. (The police stopped all the cars on the road.)